    {
      "id": "1170692781216378960",
      "name": "🔸morimens-game-chat",
      "type": 0,
      "parent_id": "1433512102714413146",
      "position": 31,
      "topic": "These rules are designed to keep the channel focused and easy to read, ensuring that only relevant game information is posted.\n\n1. Stay 100% On-Topic\n\nThis channel is strictly for in-game chat, updates, and related discussion.\nDo not post: Memes, general greetings, off-topic conversations, self-promotion, or anything that isn't directly related to the current game topic.\n\n2. No Toxicity or Rage\n\nThis channel is for factual game chat, not venting frustration or blaming other members. Keep the tone helpful and positive. Take personal conflicts to DMs or another channel.\n\n3. Follow Server-Wide Rules\n\nAll general server rules (no hate speech, no NSFW content, be respectful, etc.) are still in effect here.\n\n4. Follow Moderator Directions\n\nIf a moderator moves your message to a different channel or asks you to stop an off-topic discussion, please comply immediately.\n\nConsequences: Off-topic messages will be deleted, and repeated violations may result in timeouts or a ban from the server."
    },
