      "topic": "1. Stay 100% On-Topic\n\nThis channel is strictly for asking and answering game-related questions. Please take general discussions, memes, or other topics to their designated channels.\n\n2. Be Patient and Respectful\nOur community is here to help voluntarily. Be patient when waiting for a response, and treat everyone with respect. \n\n3. Follow Server-Wide Rules\n\nAll general server rules (no hate speech, no NSFW content, be respectful, etc.) are still in effect here.\n\n4. No Cheating or Piracy Discussions\nDo not ask for or share information about game hacks, cheats, exploits, or pirated content. These discussions are strictly prohibited across the entire server. \n\nConsequences: Messages that violate these rules may be removed, and repeat offenders could face timeouts or further moderation action."
