      "parent_id": "1437857872011726879",
      "position": 43,
      "topic": "This channel is dedicated to connecting with other members of our mobile gaming community! Please follow these simple rules to keep things organized and helpful for everyone:\n\nRules for Posting:\n\nBe Specific: Please clearly state your UID and give a screenshot of your Keepers Archive. You may access this by clicking your in-game avatar found in the top left of the main menu.\n\nNo Spamming: Only post your request once. Do not repeatedly paste your information.\n\nStay Relevant: This channel is strictly for friend requests. \n\nDo not post general chat, game results, or off-topic content here.\n\nBe Respectful: All server rules apply here. Be polite when adding others and interacting with posts."
