      "parent_id": "1437857872011726879",
      "position": 42,
      "topic": "This is your dedicated spot to show off your achievements, lucky pulls, and some bragging rights.\n\nWhat you can \"flex\" here:\n🏆 Achievements & Milestones: Hit a new rank? Finally beat that tough level? Let us know!\n\n💎 Gacha Pulls: Did you finally snag that ultra-rare character/item? Share your luck (or commiserate over a bad pull)!\n\n⚔️ Highlights & Screenshots: Post your best gameplay moments.\n\n🎉 Event Progress: Show off how far you've gotten in the current event.\n\nA couple of quick rules for the channel:\n\nBe respectful: Celebrate others' wins and be kind when they share their losses.\n\nKeep it clean: Follow all general <#1131837874078232597> \n\nNo spamming: Use this channel for sharing content, not constant chatter (we have designated channels for this)."
